dct_title_s: Reisen in Kurdistan 1910 : nach den eigenen Photographien und Routenaufnahmen / konstruirt und gezeichnet von Dr. Heinrich Freiherrn v. Handel-Mazzetti.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Red lines in main map shows the routes followed by the members of the expedition. Map shows: author's itinerary with read lines; photograph recording and photogrammetric survey points; telegraph stations; water sources not  recorded. Inset maps I-III are large scale maps of area of study. Ancillary map II: Der Meleto Dagh 1:125.000. In lower left margin: "Leitung: Prof.Paul Langhans." In lower right margin: "Autogr. von C. Schmidt." Original map  is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center. A map reproduction is attached to companion volume.
